  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You seek to lead others through your pious example.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Be a member of House Zespire, or have the Devoted, Exemplar, Marked by the Gods, or Righteous Mentor background.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Once per day as a standard action, you can give all allies within 30 feet who can hear you a +1 bonus on attack rolls and on saving throws against mind-affecting effects for 1 minute.<br/><br/><b>Goal</b><br/> Establish your religion in an existing settlement where it isn't present. You can do this by having a settlement gain the Holy Site or Pious quality for devotion to your deity, or change its government to a theocracy based on your religion.<br/><br/><b>Completion Benefit</b><br/>You can spontaneously convert any 2nd-level or higher divine spell into enthrall and can spontaneously convert any 3rd-level or higher divine spell into suggestion.",
